.", "Ponnier kan v\u00e6re fine sommervenner, b\u00e5de for dem som kjenner dem godt fra f\u00f8r, og for dem som vil pr\u00f8ve noe nytt."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|sainntja"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "f57277f7c83f3c2ca71de99cd7c6fca047b7c4fb82f20894a553cdf20ad0744f"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-02T15:41:05.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Noen dr\u00f8mmer om \u00e5 v\u00e6re i stallen hver dag. I sommerferien g\u00e5r det an. Sainntja?! har tatt turen innom de hestefrelste. Og de ferske."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article1255709.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/newPic_6736.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/32b6f34ccb8082ece79402a2276a97871def1a42.jpg?597f4e3b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Med ponni som sommervenn -adressa.no", "Mest mulig ridning", "Stelle, kose og ri", "Det f\u00f8rste m\u00f8tet"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "32b6f34ccb8082ece79402a2276a97871def1a42"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "sainntja"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "sports"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["hest", "dag"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["martine og june helen steien", "reppe ridesenter", "hoeggen", "martine og june helen"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "ada"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["june helen", "martine h\u00f8e skaftnes", "camilla linum", "june helen steien"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/sainntja"]}, {"field